1+x+x^2+x^3+...=\frac{1}{1-x}
(\frac{1}{1-x})^{k+1}=\frac{1}{(1-x)^{k+1}}
k
\frac{1}{1-x}
k!\frac{1}{(1-x)^{k+1}} 
\frac{1}{k!}\left(\frac{1}{1-x}\right)^\text{k-th derivative}=\frac{1}{(1-x)^{k+1}}
k
k!+(k+1)!x+\frac{(k+2)!}{2!}x^2+...+\frac{(k+n)!}{n!}x^n+....
\frac{1}{(1-x)^{k+1}}=\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}{n+k\choose k}x^n
x^{n}
{n+k\choose k}
